MAIN FLOOR SHOWS OFF A SIZABLE MUDROOM AND OPENS UP TO A HUGE OPEN EAT-IN KITCHEN THAT OVERLOOKS A LARGE LIVINGROOM, SEPERATE DINING ROOM/FLEX ROOM WITH A NICE-SIZED BEDROOM ON THE MAIN FLOOR!!! SECOND FLOOR BOASTS 5 BEDROOMS AND 4 FULL BATHROOMS!!! OWNERS SWEET OFFERS GRAND WALK IN ENSUITE WITH HIS/HERS SINKS, GARDEN TUB AND STAND UP SHOWER!!!
